Package: tidyul
Type: Package
Title: Tidy Unsupervised Learning Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Cesaire", "Tobias", email = "cesaire@sheetsolved.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for unsupervised learning analysis built on tidyverse principles.
    Provides simplified interfaces for principal component analysis (PCA), multidimensional scaling (MDS),
    ISOMAP, self-organizing maps (SOM), autoencoders, hierarchical clustering, k-means, k-medoids (PAM/CLARA),
    DBSCAN, market basket analysis, and more. All functions follow tidy data principles with extensive
    documentation and examples.
